# Plan 9: Admin Panel - Blog Management

## Goal

Build the blog management interface with a WYSIWYG editor.

## Tasks

- [x] Install **TipTap** (core, starter-kit, image extension).
- [x] Create `app/admin/blog/page.tsx` (List) and `app/admin/blog/new/page.tsx` (Editor).
- [x] Implement the Editor:
  - [x] Use **TipTap** for the rich text area.
  - [x] Use **ShadCN Button** for toolbar items (Bold, Italic, etc.).
  - [x] Use **ShadCN Input** for the post title.
- [x] Add image upload functionality within the editor.
- [x] Create Server Actions to save/update posts.
- [x] Add fields for SEO metadata and tags.
